<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-8">
      <div class="media">
        <br>
        <% avatar_url = @user.avatar_url(128) %>
        <div class="pull-left">
          <%= image_tag avatar_url, class: 'pull-left' %>
        </div>
        <small>
          <%= pluralize(@user.items.count, 'to-do items') %>
        </small>
        <div class="container">
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="media-body">
            <h2 class="media-heading pull-right ifont pull-right rp on-bottom">Did I do that?</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-4 abs"><br>
            <h4>Oh the frustration of forgetting what needs to be done!  Life is hectic.  Making to-do lists is an effective method of getting things done. If you find yourself wondering<br><strong class="ifont2">Did i do that?</strong><br> Then make a list.<br>  Begin!</strong><h4>
          </div>
          <div class="cwid  on-left floattop">
            <%= render current_user.items %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
